  <h1>What is JSON?</h1>
  <div class="artmeta"><span>By Coldwast</span><span>Updated Jun 14, 2026</span><span>6 min read</span><span class="tag">#json</span><span class="tag">#data</span><span class="tag">#web</span></div>
  <nav class="toc" id="toc"></nav>
  <figure>
    <img class="hero" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1607706189992-eae578626c86?w=1200&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Code in an editor on a screen" width="1200" height="420" loading="eager" />
